  "text": "Expected work includes : Design & Build: Collaborate with stakeholders to gather requirements, define user stories, and map out conversational flows. Develop: Use Microsoft Copilot Studio to build, configure, and refine chatbot topics, entities, and logic. Integrate: Leverage Power Automate (Flows) to connect the Bot to backend systems, databases, and APIs (e.g., retrieving user data, creating support tickets, looking up information). Leverage AI: Implement and fine -tune generative AI capabilities within Copilot Studio, such as generative answers over company data (e.g., SharePoint, internal websites) to handle a wide range of user queries dynamically. Test & Debug: Conduct thorough testing to ensure the Bot is accurate, responsive, and provides a seamless user experience.",
